snippet: One week after he won for the third time this season, Tiger Woods gets a rare weekend off. It’s the first time both he and Phil Mickelson have missed the cut in the same tournament.
abstract: Tiger Woods and Phil Mickelson miss the cut at the Greenbrier Classic in White Sulphur Springs, W Va.
lead_paragraph: One week after he won for the third time this season, Tiger Woods gets a rare weekend off. It’s the first time both he and Phil Mickelson have missed the cut in the same tournament.

headline.seo: Woods and Mickleson Miss Cut at Greenbrier Classic
